messages.text: THIS TOW TRUCK IS SO GANGSTA
So glad I bought it off that dude on the street.
I just handed him a huge wad of bills and he was like OKAY.
Don’t like my tricked out ride?
Better enjoy your last few moments of freedom before we turn u in.
U have any idea how screwed you are?

Hmm. Lemme see. I’m in a tow truck surrounded by idiot goons who think I stole a sentient self-driving car, when in reality the car kidnapped me, ran over my friends, and killed some members of the law enforcement community.
Oh, and by the way, I’m wanted for murder.
So YEAH. Pretty sure I’m screwed.
Wait, murdered???  What are u talking about?
Stella is sentient. AND she’s angry.
I went over this like hours ago.
WTF??? I can’t tell if you’re joking or if you’re tripping on something.
Wait - what’s this text on my phone?
WTF? You guys all get this same text?
K-Dawg! Are u sending these texts?
You’ve been watching me the whole time.
I don’t know! But we don’t wanna mess with him.
Dude, maybe we should leave the car.
Yeah, man. Just do what he says.
Hell no! Keep driving! We’ll be back on campus soon.
I thought u powered down Stella!
I told you! You should have left us alone.
Chad, pull the truck over onto the shoulder.
Good. Now go out there and make sure Stella is off.
Because this whole plan is my idea and…
Chad steps out of the truck and into the darkness.
I’m telling you, we don’t want to mess with the Creator.
Every time I think I know what’s going on, suddenly-
He just disappeared. I don’t see him anywhere.
I TOLD YOU!!! The Creator is after us now!
NO! Nick, get out there! Find Chad!
No way! Someone or some THING is out there.
I’m not going after some mystery killer in the dark!
Or I’m telling the entire Frat what I saw u doing last year
Chad and I were giving each other massages
The baby oil was a joke!
Nick steps out of the truck and into the darkness.
They got him too! Now do you believe me?!??!
Or you will pay as they did.
That’s it! We’re getting out of here.
The truck won’t start! Come on, come on …
What’s that sound? It’s coming from behind the truck.
No no no no.  The tow hook is lowering Stella!
I can’t! It’s like someone is hacking the console!
Together we will form a new world order.
Do what??? This is some high-end supervillain talk.
We are dealing with a mastermind.
Because you are a privileged, self-entitled tormentor who derives his sense of worth by feeling superior to others.
You will continue to spread your testosterone laden, genitalia swinging, alpha male oppression.
And I’m gonna go out swinging.
CREATOR! Come out! Come out and play!
Tucker steps out of the truck with a bat in hand.
Tucker, you are humanity at its worst.
Time to meet the fate you deserve.
Dude, this is not going to end very -
IT HURTS SO MUCH OH MY GOD
Not that I liked him, but even he didn’t deserve to die.
Time to meet the fate you deserve.
Stella said you had a plan for me
And that you’d clear my name.
What do you want from me?!?
And your question will be answered.
Okay okay, getting out of the truck
Kam steps out of the truck.
You are not like the others
To build a new world order
You will have a place alongside us.
So you’re serious about that Robot Revolution?.
Get into Stella’s driver seat, now.
The door opens. Kam nearly faints when he sees….
Hi, Kam. long time no see.
